    <p id="description"> Have you ever noticed how your phone seems to know what word you're going to type next when you're sending a message, or how Google search seems to guess what you’re about to search before you finish typing? Through Next Word Adventure, you will learn how computers guess the next word in an incomplete sentence using a technique called an N-gram model. You dive into the world of predictive text and see how it's not just magic—it uses some maths!
    </p>

